{"tid":1323842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警民合作有冇得玩","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:31:36.000Z","uid":268625,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a959db5b561d590aae89bf0593ba587668290189","tid":1323842,"uid":268625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"沙田一例 見到警察係打人搏還手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">你一反擊/還手就變成普通襲擊/拒捕/襲警</span></span><br />\n有d細路冇郁手都被人屈9襲警<br />\n5，6個差佬㩒低 撞地或牆<br />\n未入差館都已經成身傷 仲要未人告<br />\n<br />\n其實刑事落charge <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇證冇據好撚難入罪</span></span><br />\n特別新城市捉人 遊蕩 或非法集結都唔係<br />\n所以佢地要打人 迫人反抗 即刻可以拉<br />\n因為警察有傷口 有同事做人證 簡單好多<br />\n<br />\n不如 之後警察問攞身分證 你唔好問佢要委任證<br />\n直接大聲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">講阿SIR 我係良好市民 警民合作 有需要我可以同你去警署協助調查</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要大大聲 講完警民合作 警察都仲郁手時 可以有證據提告</span></span><br />\n因為你係良好市民 <br />\n<br />\n如果去到差館 落口供就話冇野講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時可以走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察凶你阻差辦公時，你可以同阿sir講，因為你需要我協助調查所以我黎左差館，已經好合作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係放 一係扣48小時 中間有咩損傷 記得之後驗傷 同民事訴訟<br />\n<br />\n要錢 就眾壽啦！我願課金！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要唔好俾警察打到爆血，警民合作可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 呢個玩法唔適合超級勇武戰士，和理非或半勇武可以用！"},{"pid":"9944fe351ab48a55db90188b520989db4c518b75","tid":1323842,"uid":249841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e97433ba979f5705c0a9b4839a97a5abe6997539","tid":1323842,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"冇啊"},{"pid":"5b9ef844da56bf8e8cbc150bc7953d8a37539ab8","tid":1323842,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"64ceba04f71264839812de348b8b5bed4c9f953c","tid":1323842,"uid":9466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"唔好撚on9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67feb6785d0a732598da5cb8dd979a14e406847","tid":1323842,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">合你老母！</span></span><br />\non99"},{"pid":"2815d5c8a32700b44452b33f63d8df7b5cb9d9d0","tid":1323842,"uid":268625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"去到警署佢開file 都有排做<br />\n<br />\n你去係協助調查 而唔係疑犯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9e35d9c6a9e39d7280257b145cdeae0812afa5","tid":1323842,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"On99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bcc3934fa8f70810b92c6dfadc6ea1a6bc2e4d","tid":1323842,"uid":268625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"同埋警察前線 唔係我地目標呀<br />\n<br />\n目標應該係<span style=\"font-size: xx-lar